---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Support — Neon Ninja Run" description="Support page for Neon Ninja Run. Get help with gameplay, purchases, ads, Game Center, and privacy.">
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Support</p>
    <h1>Need help with Neon Ninja Run?</h1>
    <p>Send us a clear note with your device, iOS version, and what happened. Screenshots or screen recordings help a lot.</p>
    <a class="button" href="mailto:support@neonninjarun.com">support@neonninjarun.com</a>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-content">
    <h2>Common Help Topics</h2>
    <h3>Purchases and restore</h3>
    <p>Open the Store or Premium Shop and use Restore Purchases. Make sure you are signed into the same Apple ID used for the original purchase.</p>
    <h3>Ads and rewards</h3>
    <p>Rewarded ads require a network connection and ad availability. If no ad is ready, wait a moment and try again.</p>
    <h3>Game Center</h3>
    <p>Leaderboards and achievements require Game Center to be enabled in iOS Settings.</p>
    <h3>Gameplay feedback</h3>
    <p>If a level, enemy, modifier, or reward feels wrong, include the chapter name and the mode you were playing.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
